messages.TRMSG_PRE_BATTLE: I’m a Collector, and I love Honey!
messages.TRMSG_DEFEAT:
What’ve you done to my Pokémon?!It took me forever to catch it using
Honey!
messages.TRMSG_POST_BATTLE:
I went through a lot of bother to catch
my Pokémon.But since I’ve not raised it, it’s
as weak as when I caught it.
